analysisPopulations.name: ITT population
analysisPopulations.text: Includes randomized subjects who have been documented to have suspected deleterious or deleterious mutations by the sponsor core lab. In this population subjects will be grouped according to the treatment assigned at randomization.
analysisPopulations.label: ITT
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: Includes randomized subjects who have been documented to have suspected deleterious or deleterious mutations by the sponsor core lab. In this population subjects will be grouped according to the treatment assigned at randomization.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND documented suspected deleterious or deleterious BRCA mutations by sponsor core lab

analysisPopulations.name: As-Treated population
analysisPopulations.text: Includes subjects who receive at least one dose of study drug (veliparib or placebo). In this population subjects will be grouped by the actual treatment received on the first dosing day.
analysisPopulations.label: AST
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: Includes subjects who receive at least one dose of study drug (veliparib or placebo). In this population subjects will be grouped by the actual treatment received on the first dosing day.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received at least one dose of study drug (veliparib or placebo)

analysisPopulations.name: Crossover population
analysisPopulations.text: Includes subjects who receive at least one dose of veliparib in the crossover study period.
analysisPopulations.label: Crossover
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: Includes subjects who receive at least one dose of veliparib in the crossover study period.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received at least one dose of veliparib during the crossover study period

characteristics.name: BRCA Status
characteristics.description: Core lab and historical BRCA1 and BRCA2 status

characteristics.name: ER/PgR status
characteristics.description: Estrogen receptor and/or progesterone receptor status (ER/PgR+, triple-negative)

characteristics.name: CNS Metastases
characteristics.description: Presence or absence of central nervous system metastases

characteristics.name: Prior Platinum Therapy
characteristics.description: History of prior platinum therapy use (yes versus no)

characteristics.name: ECOG Performance Status
